    <h2>
        About BrainStorm Systems</h2>
    <p>
        BrainStorm Systems is an online shell designed specifically for students to interact
        with their fellow classmates and teachers while not at school.<br /> </p>
        <hr />
        <p>
        In the design, we have incorporated several key features that helps to create a 
            better educational environment for the students.</p>
<ul>
    <li>A Chat feature for students to pose questions to one another and the teacher for 
        additional help</li> <BR>
    <li>A Grade Book feature that allows the students and their parents to see how 
        they&#39;re doing on assignments, exams, and the class overall</li> <BR>
    <li>A class Announcements feature that keeps the students up-to-date on assignment 
        due dates, upcoming exam dates, etc.</li> <BR>
    <li>A Doc Sharing feature that provides the students access to files uploaded by 
        their teachers for the day/week</li> <BR>
    <li>A Drop Box feature that provides the students an area to upload assignments as 
        they are due</li> <BR>
    <li>A Message feature that will allow the parents and teachers to communicate with 
        one another pertaining to the student&#39;s progress, etc.</li>
</ul>
